查看docker
```sh
launchctl list | grep docker

-	0	com.docker.helper
77699	0	application.com.docker.docker.739798.740119
```

关闭dockerr
```sh
launchctl stop application.com.docker.docker.739798.740119
```

启动docker

```sh
open /Applications/Docker.app
```
